{"id": "1448323862197440613", "channel_id": "1448323862197440613", "type": 0, "author_id": "702167871144591461", "author_name": "_venush", "author_bot": false, "content": "So we have all these amazing emotes that we can only use in Traphase. It would be nicer if we can use emotes to decorate our profile. And using them in PvE battles.\n\nMy reason for using emotes in PvE battles is because we have the replay feature this anni. Emotes will make watching replays more fun, more memorable and stand out. Replay is an amazing feature so I hope emotes can somehow enhance replay experience too.\n\nAnd of course, more emote usage outside of Traphase battle will encourage players to actually participate in Traphase.", "timestamp": "2025-12-10T14:41:57.304000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}], "attachments": [{"id": "1448323862545825864", "filename": "IMG_0103.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 277126, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1448323862197440613/1448323862545825864/IMG_0103.png?ex=6a009935&is=69ff47b5&hm=c529d9c510cc5767db037c30fbf644196929d544696d97ffd685f05f62529ab7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1448323862197440613", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」About emote usage: Profile decoration and PvE emotes", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1448372535816093716", "channel_id": "1448372535816093716", "type": 0, "author_id": "140102992035577856", "author_name": "pyros_", "author_bot": false, "content": "I saw a post a few weeks ago about this but just got around to using mine and noticed why the person likely had a problem.\n\nWhen selecting a character in Origin of Time, if you then scroll down all the way, it will unselect the character and select the first character in the list(Nautila for standard characters). If for example you get confused by the On Duty and scroll down, since it will select Nautila you might think it now lets you select your character and confirm without seeing it changed to her instead.\n\nAdded a short video to show the issue.\n\nhttps://youtu.be/9SdVOuS-hvQ", "timestamp": "2025-12-10T17:55:21.999000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "Morimens bug", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9SdVOuS-hvQ", "description": ""}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1448372535816093716", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Origin of Time bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
